wikipedia_page.main: Wyndham Wentworth Knatchbull-Hugessen, 3rd Baron Brabourne (21 September 1885 – 11 March 1915) was a British peer.  He was killed in action with the Grenadier Guards on 11 March 1915, and is commemorated at Le Touret.

response: * Wyndham Knatchbull-Hugessen, 3rd Baron Brabourne (1885–1915), British peer and British Army officer
